and loved pioneering together.

00:48:04.444 --> 00:48:08.072 line:90% position:50% align:center
We’ve loved every gift that we’ve been given.

00:48:10.366 --> 00:48:13.453 line:90% position:50% align:center
I tell my kids:
“Each day we live is a gift from God.

00:48:13.453 --> 00:48:16.914 line:90% position:50% align:center
How we live it is our gift to him.”

00:48:18.082 --> 00:48:20.334 line:90% position:50% align:center
The truth is only hard if we fight it.

00:48:20.334 --> 00:48:24.297 line:90% position:50% align:center
If we listen to Jehovah,
if we do what we’re asked,

00:48:24.297 --> 00:48:26.716 line:90% position:50% align:center
the blessings will catch up with us.

00:48:28.509 --> 00:48:32.263 line:90% position:50% align:center
The best day we could have here
—and we’ve all had wonderful days—

00:48:32.263 --> 00:48:36.058 line:90% position:50% align:center
is nothing in comparison
to the first day in the new world.

00:48:37.769 --> 00:48:40.688 line:90% position:50% align:center
It’s such an amazing thought

00:48:40.688 --> 00:48:43.983 line:90% position:50% align:center
to think that all we have to do
is make good choices now

00:48:43.983 --> 00:48:45.359 line:90% position:50% align:center
and then we’re going to be there!

00:48:51.532 --> 00:48:53.951 line:90% position:50% align:center
How delighted we are

00:48:53.951 --> 00:48:57.789 line:90% position:50% align:center
